{"tid":1176141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港旗設計","createTime":"2019-05-29T04:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T12:13:11.000Z","uid":218158,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b137c78aae80f590e18d8d2de9477f04ecc9f4e2","tid":1176141,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"雖則說龍獅旗的香港盾好靚，但做為一個旗幟未免太過繁複。<br />\n因此，我根據現時的區旗和以前的市政局旗幟作出更改，希望各位能夠選出你們認為最適合的。<br />\n認為都不好的可以提出意見，但請不要胡亂評論。<br />\n以下為設計時應考慮的準則：<br />\n1 .  簡單：旗幟圖案必須簡單到一個孩子能根據記憶畫出來<br />\n2 .  有意義：旗幟的圖案、色彩、圖像應當有其含義<br />\n3 .  用2-3種基本色：使得旗幟有良好的對比度<br />\n4 .  沒有文字或圖章：不要使用文字和印章<br />\n5 .  獨一無二：避免與其它旗幟相同，但可通過使用相似圖案或顏色以顯示與其的聯繫<br />\n此為被北美旗幟學協會認可的、Ted Kaye提出的五大「Good Flag, Bad Flag」原則<br />\n以下為我的三個版本：<br />\n1 .<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0r1YH0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0r1YH0.png&h=08e1204e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按照現時的區旗作出修改，由紅底改為藍底(貴族藍)，移去五星和五根線。<br />\n五根花瓣分別代表自由 , 民主 , 人權 , 法治和平等。<br />\n2 .<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaHMqqq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaHMqqq.png&h=393cd0f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按照前市政局的旗幟改成，由粉紅色改成藍底(貴族藍)，意義同上。<br />\n3 .<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7W1YL7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7W1YL7.png&h=d8b7da68&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2 . 的實心版，意義同上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主改得好，依家個抽氣扇好樣衰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收啦樓主，依家個旗不知幾靚"},{"pid":"264c880babd61f702157391d0e2ed5ee04014046","tid":1176141,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/0/0c/Liverpool_FC.svg/1200px-Liverpool_FC.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0c%2FLiverpool_FC.svg%2F1200px-Liverpool_FC.svg.png&h=d755149a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2d13d1136d6f01a8f2487e50cef3e4544f6f74f","tid":1176141,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"264c880babd61f702157391d0e2ed5ee04014046","tid":1176141,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/0/0c/Liverpool_FC.svg/1200px-Liverpool_FC.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0c%2FLiverpool_FC.svg%2F1200px-Liverpool_FC.svg.png&h=d755149a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"依個係盾嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f60a83d6ade5e24149bb194116361c88eb8492","tid":1176141,"uid":34154,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANpcam.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqANpcam.png&h=220e0f38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85e9c9a50b789e30407861ed7007257477ca7472","tid":1176141,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"32f60a83d6ade5e24149bb194116361c88eb8492","tid":1176141,"uid":34154,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANpcam.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqANpcam.png&h=220e0f38&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"太複雜喇，遠處會睇唔清楚"},{"pid":"a51180b40b7156a1ad8baaf2607226974b7fa4d8","tid":1176141,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:29:09.000Z","msg":"隻藍色好傷眼"},{"pid":"478e62a8e72ed702017d52e2ea20ebadabe7d15c","tid":1176141,"uid":70888,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29